{"tid":1642106,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】有無義工同領袖幫吓手？要比多啲人睇","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T14:33:23.000Z","uid":263448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90cbe2266eb4aa488a235d209e7917e04ed0e1e7","tid":1642106,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，依家政府打破壞同擾民牌，各位手足被深度抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日我行過交通受阻既旺角一帶，見唔到交警，但見到爛晒既路，空欄杆，爛（？）交通燈。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">明顯政府刻意唔理，造成市民對示威暴力既印象。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我做咗一陣短時間既交通指導，帶咗啲婆婆過馬路</span>，佢話唔該晒，我同佢講，我撐示威者，對唔住，佢地呆咗呆走咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實之前都有道歉同掃街既工作，依家少咗。<br />\n最近就一單一芳清潔活動咁大把。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對家打破壞牌，我地要打建設牌！！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">交通指揮，幫市民過馬路！！</span><br />\n要着反光衣，戴頭盔口罩，因為道路多塵。<br />\n記得搵幾個睇水，負責見到警察黎拉人就拍片。<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">修路</span>，有啲地下無咗一片磗，求期放啲硬淨木板比人用啦！<br />\n木板寫咩就自己隨心<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">修欄杆，就黎區選，欄杆好緊要</span>，政府怕裝完各位拎去用，所以一直無。<br />\n大家快啲用方法修！！！！<br />\n分分鐘做到<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣連儂欄杆！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小心馬路邊！！</span><br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: red;\">清潔，撕紙無手尾，我地就去清理下！</span><br />\n有啲噴到一舊舊咁好肉酸。<br />\n你去清理，無人會搞你既！清潔就梗係要口罩啦！<br />\n<br />\n5.<span style=\"color: red;\">全民衛生關注，口罩正當派發！</span><br />\n最近政府話有伊波拉病毒，仲有入侵性肺炎球菌，死咗個2歲小童，手足口病。<br />\n企係校門口、港鐵站、巴士站，派衞生常識、新聞、口罩是常識吧？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記得搵幾個社工之類既幫手，印定政府新聞出黎</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/04/P2019100400615.htm?fbclid=IwAR1fEBJScodc5TuK5cTb37hvKlL_WwnzwuF0e6M8h9Wnqe8DOm3eHtH93TY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201910%2F04%2FP2019100400615.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1fEBJScodc5TuK5cTb37hvKlL_WwnzwuF0e6M8h9Wnqe8DOm3eHtH93TY&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX51JiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=57a20b59\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201910/04/P2019100400615.htm?fbclid=IwAR1fEBJScodc5TuK5cTb37hvKlL_WwnzwuF0e6M8h9Wnqe8DOm3eHtH93TY</a>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.港鐵無車？指路員出黎啦！<br />\n好多人好懶，唔識搭巴士，有時要搵人指下路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我暫時諗到咁多，希望有組織自發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6d8f8473b396419b544a0f1335ae03dffda813","tid":1642106,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed09ca0cbd64f00e5e9ed91fcf545e67ee6736a","tid":1642106,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7bafff81a4e314af807afe392faba8ffc52b00","tid":1642106,"uid":311495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"冇人推嘅？"},{"pid":"fd583203d96bf8d564a0d6c4935044f8d92ed00c","tid":1642106,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}